Completed Today
1. TUI Dashboard Fix (Pi)
Problem: Account/positions/orders showed data (bootstrap from Alpaca), but RADAR, CRYPTO, STOCKS, regime header stayed — even at cycle 3+. Timeline showed radar events, so cycles were running — snapshots just weren’t applying to the UI.

Root cause: Background worker used call_from_thread(self._apply_snapshot, snap), which didn’t update panels on the Pi.

Fix: Switched to thread-safe post_message(StateUpdated(snap)) (same pattern as TimelineUpdated, which already worked). Removed exclusive=True from the trading worker.

Verified working: Full dashboard with regime (US CLOSED → Mon May 25 09:30 ET), RADAR table, VOL RANK, CRYPTO/STOCKS tables, AI DECISION with mood/bias, hottest command returning radar hits.

